<span id="freeTextContainer9097513875331223892">I just finished this book for our book club in St. Helens, Oregon.<br/>This is the best book I have read in years. The story is zany in a believable way and it&apos;s just full of the kind of charm and magic I wish for in my own life! We all have loss and sadness in our lives somewhere and I love how the women in this book deal with it!</span>
  <span id="freeText9097513875331223892" style="display:none">I just finished this book for our book club in St. Helens, Oregon.<br />This is the best book I have read in years. The story is zany in a believable way and it's just full of the kind of charm and magic I wish for in my own life! We all have loss and sadness in our lives somewhere and I love how the women in this book deal with it!</span>
